S.FORM: Mswati III I 1968 a miheca saka 4 folad saka 19 a romi'ad masofoc ci Mswati III, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Swazilandanini i ci Mswati III, patirengan a romi'ad i 1986 a miheca saka 4 folad saka 25 a romi'ad.
